title: The 25-26 Home Jersey
author: VD
content_html:
It looks good, especially from behind. And although automatic promotion is out due to three draws when three wins were required, they’re in the playoffs with a chance for the second spot. If you want one, let NDM know and we’ll set up a bulk US order.
